<div id="about" class="section">
    <h2>What it's all about</h2>
    <p>In every corner of the Twin Cities Metro Area there is a hacker, builder, artist, engineer,
        and entrepreneur whose efforts power the future economic vitality of this great state.
        During this week, we celebrate their efforts in the form of attention, praise, and
        investment... if you feel so bold. It's an entire week of Minnesota-made innovations on
        display.</p>
    <p>Welcome to Twin Cities Startup Week!</p>
